1649:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         synchronized with RTC APB clock.
1650:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   * @note   The RTC Resynchronization mode is write protected, use the
1651:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         __HAL_RTC_WRITEPROTECTION_DISABLE() before calling this function.
1652:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   * @note   To read the calendar through the shadow registers after Calendar
1653:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         initialization, calendar update or after wakeup from low power modes
1654:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         the software must first clear the RSF flag.
1655:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         The software must then wait until it is set again before reading
1656:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         the calendar, which means that the calendar registers have been
1657:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         correctly copied into the RTC_TR and RTC_DR shadow registers.
